data.value: select distinct T1.COLL_ID, T1.APPLIED_TO_CD, T1.COLL_DT, T1.ADJ_IND, T1.CONCURRENT_IND, T1.CRT_TYPE, T1.CST_ID, T1.CRV_ID, T1.CRD_ID, T1.OBG_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OTR_ID, T1.OTR_TYPE, T1.OTY_ID, T1.COLL_ADJ_DT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.PGM_APPLD_TO, T1.CT_ORD_APPLIED_TO, T7.CSP_SUP_NUMBER from CKT_OB_TRN T7 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_DISB_TRAN T6 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_COLLECTION T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_DISB_TRAN T4 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.CREATED_TMST <= @createdTmst) and (T1.CONCURRENT_IND = 'N') and (T1.APPLIED_TO_CD in ('C', 'G')) and ( T1.PGM_APPLD_TO not in ('AF', 'FC', 'NC', 'NF') ) and ( ( (T1.ADJ_IND = 'Y') and (T1.COLL_ADJ_DT > @collAdjDt) ) or (T1.ADJ_IND = 'N') ) and (T1.COLL_ID = T4.COL_ID) and (T1.OTY_ID = T4.OTY_ID) and (T1.OBG_ID = T4.OBG_ID) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = T4.CSP_NUMBER_DISB) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = T4.CPA_TYPE_DISB) and (T1.OTR_ID = T4.OTR_ID) and (T1.OTR_TYPE = T4.OTR_TYPE_DISB) and (T1.CRT_TYPE = T4.CRT_ID) and (T1.CST_ID = T4.CST_ID) and (T1.CRV_ID = T4.CRV_ID) and (T1.CRD_ID = T4.CRD_ID) and (T4.TYPE = 'C') and (T1.CRT_TYPE not in (2, 7)) join CKT_DISB_TRAN_RLN T5 with(readuncommitted) on (T4.DISB_TRAN_ID = T5.DTR_P_GENERATED_ID) and (T4.CPA_TYPE = T5.CPA_P_TYPE) and (T4.CSP_NUMBER = T5.CSP_P_NUMBER) on (T6.DISB_TRAN_ID = T5.DTR_GENERATED_ID) and (T6.CPA_TYPE = T5.CPA_TYPE) and (T6.CSP_NUMBER = T5.CSP_NUMBER) and (@prqGeneratedId = T6.PRQ_GENERATED_ID) on (T7.OTY_TYPE = T1.OTY_ID) and (T7.OB_TRN_TYP = T1.OTR_TYPE) and (T7.OB_TRN_ID = T1.OTR_ID) and (T7.CPA_TYPE = T1.CPA_TYPE) and (T7.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (T7.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T1.OBG_ID) and (T7.CPA_SUP_TYPE is not null) and (T7.CSP_SUP_NUMBER is not null) order by T7.CSP_SUP_NUMBER

data.name: ReadDebtAdjustment
data.value: select distinct T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OB_TRN_ID, T1.OB_TRN_TYP, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.DEBT_ADJ_TYP, T1.DEB_ADJ_DT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE, T1.OTY_TYPE from CKT_OB_TRN T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN_RLN T2 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.OTY_TYPE = T2.OTY_TYPE_SECONDARY) and (T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T2.OTR_TYPE) and (T1.OB_TRN_ID = T2.OTR_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = T2.CPA_TYPE) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = T2.CSP_NUMBER) and (T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T2.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.ONR_GENERATED_ID <> 9) and (@otyTypePrimary = T2.OTY_TYPE_PRIMARY) and (@otrPType = T2.OTR_P_TYPE) and (@otrPGeneratedId = T2.OTR_P_GENERATED_ID) and (@cpaPType = T2.CPA_P_TYPE) and (@cspPNumber = T2.CSP_P_NUMBER) and (@obgPGeneratedId = T2.OBG_P_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CREATED_TMST <= @createdTmst)

data.name: ReadDebtObligationObligationTypeDebtDetailCsePerson
data.value: select T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OB_TRN_ID, T1.OB_TRN_TYP, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE, T1.OTY_TYPE, T2.LGA_ID, T2.PRIM_SEC_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS, T4.DUE_DT from CKT_OB_TYPE T3 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OBLIGATION T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN T1 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.CREATED_TMST < @createdTmst) and (T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID = T1.OTY_TYPE) and (T2.OB_ID = T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.CPA_TYPE = T1.CPA_TYPE) and (T2.PRIM_SEC_CD <> 'S') and (@cpaSupType = T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE) and (@cspSupNumber = T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER) join CKT_DEBT_DTL T4 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.OTY_TYPE = T4.OTY_TYPE) and (T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T4.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T4.OTR_TYPE) and (T1.OB_TRN_ID = T4.OTR_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = T4.CPA_TYPE) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = T4.CSP_NUMBER) and (T4.DUE_DT between cast(@date1 as date) and cast(@date2 as date)) and (T4.DUE_DT >= @dueDt) on (T3.DEBT_TYP_ID = T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID) and (T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS = 'A') order by T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID

data.name: ReadLegalAction
data.value: select top(1) LEGAL_ACTION_ID, STANDARD_NO from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION with(readuncommitted) where LEGAL_ACTION_ID = @legalActionId

data.name: ReadLegalReferralServiceProvider
data.value: select distinct T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.IDENTIFIER, T1.STATUS_DATE, T1.STATUS, T1.REFERRAL_DATE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.REFERRAL_REASON_1, T1.REFERRAL_REASON_2, T1.REFERRAL_REASON_3, T1.REFERRAL_REASON_4, T1.COURT_CASE_NO, T1.TRB_ID, T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T2.USER_ID from CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_LEGAL_REFERRAL T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_ASSGN_LEG_REF T4 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.CAS_NUMBER = @casNumber) and ( ( (T1.STATUS in ('O', 'S')) and (T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP <= @createdTimestamp) ) or ( (T1.STATUS in ('C', 'W', 'R')) and (T1.STATUS_DATE >= @statusDate) and (T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP <= @createdTimestamp) ) ) and (T1.IDENTIFIER = T4.LGR_ID) and (T1.CAS_NUMBER = T4.CAS_NO) and (T4.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @statusDate) and (T4.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @discontinueDate) on T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T4.SPD_ID order by T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T1.STATUS_DATE desc

data.name: ReadPaymentRequest
